    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "oh okay that makes sense. but it still feels like it's causing damage or something when i feel that burn mid-set. like, what is actually happening in the moment to cause that sensation and why does it feel like it's \"clogging\" or slowing me down?",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
